### Sample requests (VS Code REST Client / IntelliJ HTTP client).
### Base URL
@base = http://localhost:8000/api
@adminKey = dev-admin-key

### Health check
GET {{base}}/health

### Ingest an inbound onboarding email (body only)
POST {{base}}/email/inbound
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="body"

Hi, I'm Rahul Sharma and I'd like to onboard. Reach me at rahul@example.com
or 9123456780. I currently stay at 45 Park Street, Mumbai.
--boundary--

### Ingest an inbound email WITH a document attachment (file upload)
### Details match the document -> approved. See samples/sample_emails.md.
POST {{base}}/email/inbound
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="body"

Name: John Doe
Email: john.doe@example.com
Phone: +91 98765 43210
Address: 45 Park Street, Andheri West, Mumbai 400058
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="attachments"; filename="aadhaar.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./samples/aadhaar_johndoe.png
--boundary--

### Mismatch: body name differs from the document -> requires_manual_review
### (also flagged as a duplicate document - run AFTER the request above)
POST {{base}}/email/inbound
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="body"

Name: Rahul Sharma
Email: rahul.sharma@example.com
Phone: 9123456780
Address: 12 MG Road, Bengaluru 560001
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="attachments"; filename="aadhaar.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./samples/aadhaar_johndoe.png
--boundary--

### Prose, no attachment -> rejected (documents missing)
POST {{base}}/email/inbound
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="body"

Hi team, I'm Priya Verma and I'd like to get onboarded. Reach me at
priya.verma@example.com or on +91 98200 11223. I stay at 21 Residency Road,
Bengaluru, Karnataka 560025.
--boundary--

### Reply threading: send the original, then the reply (maps onto the same ticket)
POST {{base}}/email/inbound
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="body"

Message-ID: <onboard-arjun-001@example.com>
From: Arjun Nair <arjun.nair@example.com>

Hi, I'd like to begin onboarding. You can reach me on 9988776655.
--boundary--

###
POST {{base}}/email/inbound
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="body"

In-Reply-To: <onboard-arjun-001@example.com>
From: Arjun Nair <arjun.nair@example.com>

Quick follow-up on my onboarding request above - thanks!
--boundary--

### List tickets (paginated, optional ?status=approved|rejected|...)
GET {{base}}/tickets

### Ticket detail (replace 1 with a real id)
GET {{base}}/tickets/1

### Ticket timeline
GET {{base}}/tickets/1/timeline

### Ticket documents
GET {{base}}/tickets/1/documents

### Update ticket status (admin - needs X-Admin-Key)
PATCH {{base}}/tickets/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
X-Admin-Key: {{adminKey}}

{ "status": "approved", "note": "manually approved" }

### Reprocess a ticket (admin)
POST {{base}}/tickets/1/reprocess
X-Admin-Key: {{adminKey}}


